Sofia,

You can set argument 'big.mark' in settings.meta() which is considered in printouts and forest plots.

events <- c(12000, 5000, 800, 30000)
n <- c(50000, 10000, 5000, 40000)

library("meta")
settings.meta(big.mark = ",")
m <- metaprop(events, n)
forest(m)

Best,
Guido


