                                                        estimate
 se             zval          pval           ci.lb            ci.ub

durS:posU  1.7890  1.4294 1.2516 0.2107 -1.0126  4.5906


(c) I use L as reference for duration, and this is the result


                            estimate       se              zval
 pval           ci.lb            ci.ub

durS:posU  1.2827  0.9275  1.3829 0.1667 -0.5352 3.1005


